name: INFINITE CHAOS | ISSUE 1/4
description:
an endless stream of random monochromatic glyphs in an infinite dance, order and chaos, darkness and light, interrupted only by unrelentless shades of grey

relax your eyes and focus on the noise while you marvel at just how small your own single configuration truly is when cast into the unknown

this is an open edition to celebrate 5k followers. remaining copies will be burnt in 36 hours, and the number of remaining editions will be used as an input variable in a future nft
